SECURITY LEVEL: Company defined Member access to Documents, Q&A, Projects, etc. (for example: 0=everyone, 1=non-employees 2=employees, 3=supervisors, 4=managers, 5=executives, etc.). Each Member can access information at his Security Level and lower.

LIMITS: Access to the system can be limited by IP address (IP:), day of week (DAY:), or by time of day (TIME:). For example, IP:1.2.3 (any IP address starting with 1.2.3) --OR-- DAY:17 (weekend only) --OR-- TIME:900-1700 (9:00am - 5:00pm) Multiple limits are delimited with a semicolon. NONE designates no limits. IPL:1-4 designates the level of IP tracking. Access to Quizes can also be limited to no retakes or no answers and no retakes.
